OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud around eastern
OL,6,Fcoasts but mostly fine and dry to
OL,7,Fstart. Cloud breaks rapidly to a sunny
OL,8,Fand hot day across much of the area
OL,9,Fwith a low risk of an isolated shower
OL,10,Fdeveloping later. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening for most with
OL,13,Fany showers easing. Cloud potentially
OL,14,Fbuilding more widely across the area
OL,15,Fbut remaining dry. Light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudier start but quickly
OL,18,Fbreaking through the morning. Cooler
OL,19,Fthan recent days but remaining fine
OL,20,Ffor most with a low risk of isolated
OL,21,Fshowers developing later. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
